*http-replicator-3.0-r4 (22 Dec 2013)

  22 Dec 2013; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> +files/http-replicator.service,
  +files/http-replicator.service.conf, +http-replicator-3.0-r4.ebuild,
